description: For sale: $649,000. This is an exclusive, 6 year old, custom designed/built home that is SUPER Insulated with foam insulation AND also radiates with character and craftsmanship.  It boasts many features which will help provide total enjoyment of this property.  The home has a  stately exterior design, and is nestled into a nicely wooded and rolling, 2 acre setting.  The tree-lined, circular driveway completes a beautiful picture of this property which is located in the executive,  neighborhood of Wyldewood Acres - complete with sidewalks!  Inside, the main level easy-living floor plan includes hand-scraped Acacia hardwood floors, Knotty Alder cabinets with granite tops, the Great Room with vaulted, collar-tied beamed ceiling, a commanding stone-faced fireplace, and the all-important Master Suite, just to mention a few.  This property must be seen to appreciate the entire package, which includes Scandia Elementary school being "just around the corner"!  Sept. - March Nat. Gas cost averages $102 per month!

For sale: $539,000. This beautifully maintained classic Dutch colonial is on 6+ gorgeous acres of lawn, mature trees & open space in a quiet neighborhood overlooking William O'Brien Park in the St. Croix Valley. Up-to-date with desirable features like shiplap walls & pine flooring in the family room. Recent upgrades: roof, gutters & guard; Andersen windows & patio door; fresh paint in and out; kitchen counter, floor; bath sinks; bedroom carpet; much more. All measurements from blueprint. See photos & supplement. Home Warranty Included.

For sale: $650,000. Wow! Own a slice of paradise for you and your horses! Beautiful 2 story features a granite kitchen, hardwood floors, wood burning fireplace, formal DR, locked off main floor mother-in-law or owners suite. This makes for main level living if desired! Upstairs master bedroom has large dressing room that could be converted back to 5th bedroom! Lower level offers a finished recreation/family room. Large barn with 4 stalls, paddock for cows if desired, outdoor riding ring, 2 pastures, large turn around driveway for large trailers, separate driveway to the barn but still walkable! The little landlocked lake was once stocked by the DNR with walley!  Put in a little dock and some kayaks and enjoy the nature!  Great trails nearby via Wild River State Park & Pine Pointe, Gateway, etc. Scandia Riders Club nearby and more!  Country living just north of the twin cities!

description:
Recently sold: $550,000. Welcome to 14201 209th Street in desirable Wyldewood Acres in Scanida.  This neighborhood offers the best of both worlds -- larger, pravte lots with paved streets and sidewalks, while still walking distance to Scandia Elementary, parks, church, store, and restaurants.  The two acre lot offers plenty of space for kids and pets to play and has beautiful long views.  There is a great bonfire area off to the side of the home that is ideal for summer evenings and neighborhood get-togethers.  This home has a large maintenance free deck, upgraded steel siding, front porch, and an amazing 4-car garage plus a large heated shop area, too!

Step inside and you will enjoy the main floor that features an office, formal and informal living and dining areas, custom maple cabinets, red birch hardwood floors, and a great sun room that also steps out to the backyard deck.  The upper level has an amazing five bedrooms, three bathrooms, laundry, AND a huge finished bonus room that is set up as a theater room.  The master bedroom features a private bath with whirlpool tub, shower, and walk-in closet.

Now retreat down to the lower level and be amazed and one of the best family room/man caves you will ever see!  The lower level features custom cherry wood trim details throughout including paneled walls, built-ins, crown moulding, and a complete, impressive full bar.  The area is set up great for card or poker nights, plus just a great place to relax in front of the fire and take in a game on the big screen.  The lower level is completed with the 6th bedroom plus a stunning 3/4 bathroom with cherry cabinets, custom stone tile walk-in shower, and a sauna.

This one really has it all!  Set up a showing to see this one today!
